{"tid":783193,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"禍根是「不執法」","createTime":"2018-08-17T10:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T10:59:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a2ba5ef2c0a5e37b4dc6d7c4883b4ce7874a022a","tid":783193,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:56:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20180817/20477904\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180817%2F20477904&d=bO0u9ZGjfLMWtTGwNArufGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=967fc4bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180817%2F20477904&h=1a4d3b0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20180817/20477904</a><br />\n<br />\n禍根是「不執法」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180817/large/1534404088_1219.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180817%2Flarge%2F1534404088_1219.jpg&h=8813dc83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n神憎鬼厭人怨怒的大媽歌舞團，自大陸各省市，至香港屯門、旺角菜街、尖沙咀、銅鑼灣、時代廣場&hellip;&hellip;如惡毒癌細胞擴散，全港流竄。政府各部門互相推卸，曾「打賞」丐幫大媽$500的777，做完政治show還好意思驅蝗嗎？保安無力，警方無實際行動，致令這些大媽面對禁制令，警告信、示威者圍轟&hellip;&hellip;也面不改容，「我中意唱就唱！」<br />\n<br />\n沒轍？只因「不執法」。對阿公阿婆和看不順眼的反對派，又拉又鎖又判監，對文革陰魂就「畏縮」不前，欺善怕惡！事實上大媽也欺善怕惡，對付方法並不難：──<br />\n<br />\n（一）她們噪音擾民，污染環境，影響市民生活，全靠揚聲器，分貝一超標就沒收（如小販貨物），一招了。<br />\n<br />\n（二）禁止非法「行乞」、「打賞」（收、受皆有問題）──冇錢，還姣屍扽篤歌舞撩客？遑論散檔後的「服務」了。<br />\n<br />\n（三）放蛇。既然大媽客路都是些鹹濕伯父，便找一批將近退休的阿sir扮老淫蟲，證據確鑿依法辦事。<br />\n<br />\n（四）&hellip;&hellip;（請大家提出）<br />\n其實最最最主要的禍根，就是不──執──法。不殺一儆百哪會斷尾？且根據保安局局長李家超公告：任何一人以上組織都視為社團，根據社團條例執法，有所行動，別雙重標準！  <br />\n<br />\n李碧華 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n不能只識工程 (左丁山)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n冰島遇同胞 (李純恩)"},{"pid":"97182c951e8295994fae55691b58a8b90b9eda56","tid":783193,"uid":81716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:59:34.000Z","msg":"咁雲根係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}